## Key API Endpoints

### Research (Phase 7)
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | `/api/v1/research/start` | Start autonomous research |
| GET | `/api/v1/research/{id}` | Get research status/results |
| GET | `/api/v1/research/history` | List research history |
| GET | `/api/v1/research/status` | System capacity & active executions |

### Watchlists (Phase 7)
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | `/api/v1/watchlists` | Create watchlist (5 types) |
| GET | `/api/v1/watchlists` | List watchlists |
| GET | `/api/v1/watchlists/{id}` | Get watchlist details |
| POST | `/api/v1/watchlists/{id}/companies` | Add company |
| DELETE | `/api/v1/watchlists/{id}/companies/{symbol}` | Remove company |
| POST | `/api/v1/watchlists/{id}/alerts` | Create alert rule |

### Approvals (Phase 7)
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| GET | `/api/v1/approval/{id}` | Get approval request |
| POST | `/api/v1/approval/{id}/action` | Process approval action |
| GET | `/api/v1/approval` | List approval requests |

### Reports (Phase 7)
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | `/api/v1/reports/generate` | Generate report (8 types, 3 formats) |
| GET | `/api/v1/reports` | List generated reports |

### Copilot (Phase 8)
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | `/api/v1/copilot/chat` | Natural language chat (SSE streaming) |
| POST | `/api/v1/copilot/sessions` | Create session |
| GET | `/api/v1/copilot/sessions` | List sessions |
| POST | `/api/v1/copilot/sessions/{id}/plan` | Create execution plan |
| POST | `/api/v1/copilot/sessions/{id}/execute` | Execute plan |
| GET | `/api/v1/copilot/tools` | List available tools |
| POST | `/api/v1/copilot/tools/execute` | Execute specific tool |
| GET | `/api/v1/copilot/sessions/{id}/history` | Session history |
| GET | `/api/v1/copilot/sessions/{id}/status` | Session status |

### Health (Phase 6)
| Endpoint | Purpose |
|----------|---------|
| `GET /health` | Basic liveness |
| `GET /health/live` | Kubernetes liveness probe |
| `GET /health/ready` | Kubernetes readiness probe |
| `GET /health/detailed` | Full component health |
| `GET /metrics` | Prometheus metrics (30+) |

