## Authentication & Authorization

### JWT (RS256)
```python
# Header
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

# Payload
{
  "sub": "user123",
  "roles": ["analyst"],
  "permissions": ["research:create", "research:read", "watchlist:*"],
  "exp": 1705564800
}
```

### API Key
```bash
# Header
X-API-Key: fra_live_abc123def456...

# Or query param (less secure)
?api_key=fra_live_abc123def456...
```

### RBAC Permissions
| Role | Permissions |
|------|-------------|
| `admin` | All (`*`, `admin:*`) |
| `analyst` | `research:*`, `watchlist:*`, `report:*`, `approval:*`, `copilot:*` |
| `viewer` | `research:read`, `watchlist:read`, `report:read`, `copilot:chat` |
| `api_only` | `research:create`, `research:read`, `copilot:chat`, `copilot:plan` |

