## Error Response Format

```json
{
  "error": {
    "code": "VALIDATION_ERROR",
    "message": "Invalid input parameters",
    "details": [
      {"field": "company", "message": "Company ticker required"}
    ],
    "request_id": "req_abc123"
  }
}
```

| HTTP Code | Meaning |
|-----------|---------|
| 200 | Success |
| 201 | Created |
| 202 | Accepted (async) |
| 400 | Bad Request |
| 401 | Unauthorized |
| 403 | Forbidden |
| 404 | Not Found |
| 422 | Validation Error |
| 429 | Rate Limited |
| 500 | Internal Error |
| 503 | Service Unavailable |

